{"tid":2231692,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國一戰機空中撞鳥停機","createTime":"2020-10-06T00:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T00:39:35.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6037507908ed4a69009dfb857f8a9fd26ddf64b6","tid":2231692,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:09:40.000Z","msg":"中國一戰機空中撞鳥停機<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201005-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%AD%E6%92%9E%E9%B3%A5%E5%81%9C%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20201005-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2592%259E%25E9%25B3%25A5%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25A9%259F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=73774fea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201005-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%AD%E6%92%9E%E9%B3%A5%E5%81%9C%E6%A9%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n中國官方媒體稱，中國一名飛行員所駕駛的戰機低空遭鳥撞擊後在空中停車，戰機快速下降，但飛行員37秒內三次規避居民區，沒有造成人員傷亡。消息沒有提及涉案飛機說直升飛機還是其他類型戰鬥機。<br />\n<br />\n據聯合早報今天引述消息說，中國戰機撞鳥後停車，飛行員三次規避居民區。消息稱，據中國《解放軍報》今天（5日）報道，中國解放軍南部戰區空軍航空兵某旅飛行員王建東事發前駕機升空，開展對抗空戰訓練。<br />\n<br />\n據中國媒體描述，兩道黑影突然迎面飛速閃過，隨着&ldquo;砰&rdquo;的一聲，機身猛然一震，發動機工作出現異常。王建東迅速向指揮員報告戰機撞鳥，指揮員則提醒王建東：&ldquo;注意保持，檢查發動機工作。&rdquo;中國官方媒體報道稱，話音剛落，座艙內告警聲急促響起，飛機推力急劇下降。王建東再次推油門，飛機卻沒有一點&ldquo;擡頭&rdquo;跡象。<br />\n<br />\n戰機遭鳥撞擊時，戰機距離地面只有272.7米，不具備場內迫降條件。王建東操控戰機右轉以避開市區，並努力保持戰機狀態，儘可能滑翔得更遠，同時緊急搜索空地。<br />\n<br />\n戰機發動機隨後停車，飛機完全失去動力，所幸王建東找到並對準水田，讓戰機墜地。王建東最終降落在一座果園，幾位村民發現後，將他擡到樹蔭下，等待救護。<br />\n<br />\n報道未提及事發時間和地點。也沒有提及戰機是否有彈射飛行員裝置以及飛機墜毀狀況。"},{"pid":"bd52ca8bbe9592acaff42f5f591ff04d206e0081","tid":2231692,"uid":374180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:10:44.000Z","msg":"睇錯一戰戰機<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0770dec7334aa78b72d9877392673e592e09720b","tid":2231692,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:26:44.000Z","msg":"成日笑台灣墜機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3868bf75efce85b5bd555fd44b1aadbc96bfc8d7","tid":2231692,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365da0796f50f8cc48e5911cdd6523550ad6dfec","tid":2231692,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd52ca8bbe9592acaff42f5f591ff04d206e0081","tid":2231692,"uid":374180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:10:44.000Z","msg":"睇錯一戰戰機<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:35:43.000Z","msg":"我都get 到係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7e179ab1f955fdb6d8ea0b1f403b83da85dbfc","tid":2231692,"uid":224882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:39:35.000Z","msg":"cctvb報呢單果陣好強調個機師避開民居先跳傘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}